######### execute-stop #########
Sends a stop command to the robot

Examples:
	Stop.
	
## Arguments
none

## Output Command (copied as current-action.stop-command)
^do-control-law
	^name stop
	^termination-condition
		^name stabilized
		
## Operators

send-stop-command - puts the command on the output link
report-success    - proposed when the command finishes, marks current-action.status complete	